<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="it">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>Bollettino Marca da Bollo — {{ app_entity.name|default('Ente') }}</title>
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; }
    body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: #1a1a1a; margin: 0; padding: 0; background: #f0f2f5; }
    .page { max-width: 620px; margin: 32px auto; background: #fff; border: 1px solid #ccc; border-radius: 6px; padding: 32px; }
    .header { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 16px; border-bottom: 3px solid #0066cc; padding-bottom: 16px; margin-bottom: 24px; }
    .header-logo-box { width: 56px; height: 56px; flex-shrink: 0; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; background: #0066cc; border-radius: 8px; color: #fff; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; overflow: hidden; }
    .header-logo-box img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: contain; }
    .header-text h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; color: #0066cc; }
    .header-text p { margin: 4px 0 0; font-size: 12px; color: #666; }
    .badge-mbt { display: inline-block; background: #0066cc; color: #fff; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; padding: 2px 10px; border-radius: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.05em; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .importo-box { text-align: center; border: 2px solid #0066cc; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; margin-bottom: 24px; background: #f0f6ff; }
    .importo-box .lbl { font-size: 12px; color: #555; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em; margin-bottom: 6px; }
    .importo-box .amount { font-size: 40px; font-weight: 700; color: #0066cc; line-height: 1; }
    .fields { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 14px; margin-bottom: 24px; }
    .field .lbl { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; color: #888; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; margin-bottom: 2px; }
    .field .val { font-size: 13px; color: #1a1a1a; word-break: break-all; font-family: monospace; }
    .field.full { grid-column: 1 / -1; }
    .field.full .val { font-family: inherit; }
    .qr-section { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 24px; border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0; padding-top: 24px; margin-top: 24px; }
    #qrcode-wrap { flex-shrink: 0; background: #fff; padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 4px; }
    #qrcode-wrap canvas, #qrcode-wrap img { display: block; }
    .qr-info { flex: 1; }
    .qr-info h2 { margin: 0 0 8px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; }
    .qr-info p { margin: 0 0 8px; font-size: 12px; color: #555; line-height: 1.5; }
    .qr-string { font-family: monospace; font-size: 10px; color: #888; word-break: break-all; background: #f5f5f5; padding: 5px 7px; border-radius: 4px; margin-top: 6px; }
    .actions { text-align: center; margin-top: 28px; }
    .btn-print { background: #0066cc; color: #fff; border: none; padding: 11px 28px; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer; }
    .btn-print:hover { background: #0052a3; }
    .footer-note { margin-top: 24px; font-size: 11px; color: #aaa; border-top: 1px solid #e8e8e8; padding-top: 12px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5; }
    @media print {
      body { background: #fff; }
      .page { margin: 0; border: none; border-radius: 0; padding: 16px; max-width: 100%; }
      .actions { display: none !important; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="page">

  <div class="header">
    <div class="header-logo-box">
      {% if app_logo is defined and app_logo.type == 'img' and app_logo.src is defined %}
        <img src="{{ app_logo.src }}" alt="">
      {% else %}
        {{ app_entity.name|default('E')|slice(0,1)|upper }}
      {% endif %}
    </div>
    <div class="header-text">
      <h1>{{ app_entity.name|default('Ente') }}</h1>
      <p>Bollettino pagoPA — Marca da Bollo Telematica</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div><span class="badge-mbt">MARCA DA BOLLO TELEMATICA</span></div>

  <div class="importo-box">
    <div class="lbl">Importo da pagare</div>
    <div class="amount">€ {{ importoEur }}</div>
  </div>

  <div class="fields">
    <div class="field">
      <div class="lbl">Numero avviso (IUV)</div>
      <div class="val">{{ iuv }}</div>
    </div>
    <div class="field">
      <div class="lbl">Codice ente</div>
      <div class="val">{{ ente }}</div>
    </div>
    {% if causale %}
    <div class="field full">
      <div class="lbl">Causale</div>
      <div class="val">{{ causale }}</div>
    </div>
    {% endif %}
    {% if cfDeb %}
    <div class="field">
      <div class="lbl">Soggetto pagatore</div>
      <div class="val">{{ cfDeb }}</div>
    </div>
    {% endif %}
    {% if scadenza %}
    <div class="field">
      <div class="lbl">Scadenza</div>
      <div class="val">{{ scadenza }}</div>
    </div>
    {% endif %}
  </div>

  <div class="qr-section">
    <div id="qrcode-wrap">
      <div id="qrcode"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="qr-info">
      <h2>Paga con il QR code</h2>
      <p>Scansiona il codice con l'<strong>app IO</strong> o con un <strong>terminale POS abilitato pagoPA</strong> per avviare il pagamento.</p>
      <p>In alternativa, vai su <strong>pagopa.gov.it</strong> e inserisci il numero avviso e il codice ente sopra indicati.</p>
      <div class="qr-string" id="qrStringDisplay">{{ qrString }}</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="actions">
    <button class="btn-print" onclick="window.print()">🖨 Stampa / Salva come PDF</button>
  </div>

  <div class="footer-note">
    Bollettino generato da {{ app_entity.name|default('Ente') }} tramite il circuito ufficiale pagoPA.<br>
    Conserva la ricevuta di pagamento come prova dell'avvenuto versamento.
  </div>

</div>

{# TODO: bundle qrcodejs inline (npm install qrcodejs, then copy qrcode.min.js here) for offline/CSP environments #}
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/qrcodejs@1.0.0/qrcode.min.js"></script>
<script>
(function(){
  var qrString = {{ qrString|json_encode }};
  var el = document.getElementById('qrcode');
  if (el && typeof QRCode !== 'undefined') {
    new QRCode(el, {
      text: qrString,
      width: 160,
      height: 160,
      colorDark: '#000000',
      colorLight: '#ffffff',
      correctLevel: QRCode.CorrectLevel.M
    });
  } else if (el) {
    el.innerHTML = '<p style="font-size:11px;color:#c00;">QR non disponibile (nessuna connessione).<br>Usa il numero avviso sopra.</p>';
  }
})();
</script>
</body>
</html>
